        "title": "Convert file path to URI object emf.common.util.URI",
        "body": "<p>I need a solution to convert file path to EMF URI, not a Java URI.<\/p>\n\n<p>I tried with this:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>org.eclipse.emf.common.util.URI ur = org.eclipse.emf.common.util.URI.createURI(URI.createURI(file.getPath()).toString());\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>...but  I get this exception:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>java.net.MalformedURLException: unknown protocol: c appears .\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Is there another solution?<\/p>\n",
